			Profile
			
			QiangZHENGgraduatedfromDepartmentofChemistry,ZhejiangUniversityin1982.Asanassistantengineer,hedidresearchonsynthesisandmodificationofsiliconrubbermaterialsatTheChenguangResearchInstituteofChengguangChemicalIndustry,China,from1982to1985.HegotmasterdegreeatDepartmentofPolymerMaterials&amp;Engineering,ChengduUniversityofScienceandTechnology(CUST)in1988andthenjoinedthePolymerResearchInstituteofCUST.AfterfinishedhisPhDcoursesinCUST,hewenttoKyotoUniversitytocontinuehisPhDprogramfrom1992to1994.HegotPhDdegreeatPolymerResearchInstituteofSichuanUniversityintheendof1994.Hebecameaassociateprofessorandafullprofessorin1995and1998respectively,intheDepartmentofPolymerScienceandEngineering,ZhejiangUniversity.Heteachestwomasteranddoctorcoursesrelatedtopolymerstructure&amp;propertiesandpolymerrheologyandisthetutorforthePhDandMScdegreesinpolymermaterials&amp;polymerprocessing,respectively.
Hisresearchinterestsareinthepolymerrheology,structure-propertiesrelationshipformulti-componentpolymericmaterialsandfunctionalpolymericmaterials.Especiallytherelationshipbetweenspecialdynamicviscoelasticalbehavioratlowfrequencies(longtimeregion)andphase&ndash;separation,rheologicalbehaviorandfunctionalpropertiesarehisrepresentativeresearchsubjects.HegotalotofhonourandawardsincludingNationalScienceFoundsforDistinguishedYoungScholarsin2001andChangJiang(CheungKong)Scholarsin2004.Besides,heholdsalotofpostsconcurrentlyincludingthememberofScience-technologyCommitteeofNationalEducationDepartment,thememberofcouncilofChemistrySociety,China,thememberofPolymerScienceCommitteeofChinaandmemberofRheologyAssociationofChina.AndheisalsoattheeditorialboardofChinesefamousacademyperiodicalssuchasChineseScienceBulletin,ChineseJournalofPolymerScience,ChineseJournalofAppliedChemistry,FunctionalMaterial,JournalofMaterialsScienceandEngineering,PolymerBulletin,ChinaPlasticsIndustry.RecentlyhebecametheregionaleditorofTheJournaloftheSocietyofRheology.Japan.Uptonow,hehaspublished220papersininternationaljournalssuchasMacromolecular,Polymer,JournalofPolymerScience,PolymerPhysics:PartB,MacromolecularChemistryandPhysics,ChineseJ.Polym.Sci.andJ.Mater.Res.,etc.
			
				
